Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Stops an ongoing effect.

Usage
-----

*void* stopEffect( *string* **effectName** )

Parameters
----------

-   [effectName] - Name of effect to stop.

Examples
--------

<font color="#000055">`$my_entity`</font>`.`<font color="#ff0000">`stopEffect`</font><font color="#000000">`(`</font>` `<font color="#666666">`"fire64"`</font>` `<font color="#000000">`)`</font>`;`

Notes
-----

This script event does not return any values. See the [PlayEffect](PlayEffect\_(script\_event)) event.


